## ğŸ”§ Configuration

To add custom hyperparameters, simply pass them as a dictionary:

```python
custom_params = {
    'alpha': [0.01, 0.1, 1, 10],
    'solver': ['auto', 'svd', 'cholesky']
}
perform_grid_search('Ridge', X_train_scaled, y_train, additional_params=custom_params)
```

